               fined 1s.
            </rs>
               </p>
               <p>Wood, <rs id="t17970712-27-verdict146" type="verdictDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17970712-27-verdict146" type="verdictCategory" value="notGuilty"></interp>
               NOT GUILTY
